h-56px)]\"><nav class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-4\"><div class=\"space-y-1\"><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🏠</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">首页</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">概览与推荐</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/skill\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">✨</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Skill</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">可复用的能力模块</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/mcp\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🔌</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">MCP</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">外部工具与服务接入</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/agent\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🤖</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Agent</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">自主决策的AI助手</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/prompt\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">📝</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Prompt</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">高效沟通的模板</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/workflow\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🔄</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Workflow</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">多步骤任务编排</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/knowledge\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🗃️</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Knowledge</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">企业知识智能检索</div></div></a></div></nav><div class=\"shrink-0 p-4 border-t border-gray-100 bg-white\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400\"><div>版本 v1.0.0</div><div class=\"mt-1\">© 2026 AI Tools Center</div></div></div></aside><main class=\"flex-1 ml-72\"><div class=\"p-8\"><nav class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6\"><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn\">学院</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn/path/architect\">架构师路径</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-gray-900 font-medium\">企业级实践</span></nav><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-600 to-gray-700 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-4xl\"></span><div><h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">企业级实践</h1><p class=\"text-white/80\">企业级架构设计</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 text-white/80 text-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>预计 <!-- -->85分钟</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>架构师路径</span></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><span class=\"text-gray-500\">难度选择：</span><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/production/beginner\">入门路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/production/developer\">开发者路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-blue-600 text-white\" href=\"/learn/production/architect\">架构师路径</a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8\"><div class=\"prose prose-gray max-w-none\"><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">1</span>多租户架构设计</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3\">什么是多租户？</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-700\">多租户架构让多个客户/部门共享同一套基础设施，但数据完全隔离。SaaS 产品的标准架构。</p><div class=\"mt-3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-green-600\">共享资源</p><ul class=\"text-xs text-gray-600 space-y-1 mt-2\"><li>• 应用服务器</li><li>• 负载均衡</li><li>• 缓存集群</li><li>• 监控系统</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-blue-600\">隔离资源</p><ul class=\"text-xs text-gray-600 space-y-1 mt-2\"><li>• 数据库 Schema/Database</li><li>• 向量 Collection</li><li>• API Key</li><li>• 配置和权限</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">隔离策略</h5><div class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-700\">行级隔离（简单）</p><p class=\"text-gray-600\">每个租户共享数据库表，通过 tenant_id 区分</p><p class=\"text-xs text-green-600\">优点：成本低 | 缺点：安全风险</p></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-700\">Schema 隔离（推荐）</p><p class=\"text-gray-600\">每个租户独立的 Schema，物理隔离</p><p class=\"text-xs text-green-600\">优点：安全性高 | 缺点：中等成本</p></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-700\">Database 隔离（高安全）</p><p class=\"text-gray-600\">每个租户独立数据库，完全隔离</p><p class=\"text-xs text-green-600\">优点：最高安全 | 缺点：成本最高</p></div></div></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-purple-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">配额与计费</h5><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1\"><li>• 每个租户独立的配额：QPS、Token 数、存储空间</li><li>• 精细化计费：按租户、按功能、按用户维度</li><li>• 配额超限处理：拒绝、排队、降级</li><li>• 账单系统：定期生成、邮件通知、逾期提醒</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">2</span>可扩展架构设计</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"p-3 bg-green-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">水平扩展策略</h5><div class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-700\">无状态服务</p><p class=\"text-gray-600\">服务不保存会话状态，任何节点都能处理请求</p></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-700\">弹性伸缩</p><p class=\"text-gray-600\">根据负载自动扩缩容节点，节省成本</p><p class=\"text-xs text-green-600\">技术：K8s HPA / 云厂商自动伸缩组</p></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-700\">负载均衡</p><p class=\"text-gray-600\">均匀分发流量，避免单点过载</p><p class=\"text-xs text-green-600\">算法：轮询 / 加权轮询 / 最少连接</p></div></div></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-orange-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">数据分片策略</h5><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1\"><li>• <strong>用户路由</strong>：同一用户的所有请求路由到同一节点，复用缓存</li><li>• <strong>功能路由</strong>：不同功能的请求分发到专用节点池</li><li>• <strong>地理路由</strong>：按用户地理位置路由到最近的节点</li><li>• <strong>成本路由</strong>：不同成本的任务路由到不同规格的节点</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-700\">云服务对比</h4><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2\"><div><strong>Serverless（无服务器）</strong>：Lambda / Cloud Functions - 适合低频、突发流量</div><div><strong>容器服务</strong>：ECS / GKE / AKS - 适合持续稳定流量</div><div><strong>虚拟机</strong>：EC2 / VM - 适合完全控制需求</div><div><strong>托管服务</strong>：Vercel / Cloudflare Workers - 适合前端应用</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn/path/architect\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M15 19l-7-7 7-7\"></path></svg>返回<!-- -->架构师路径</a><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn\">返回学院<svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main></div></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0j6kpnbwgrhei.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[30824,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"Providers\\\"]\\n3:I[87161,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"